name: MyNetResearch
tag_list: research-management, research-collaboration, online-survey, find-researchers, citation-tools, research-methods
overview:
MyNetResearch.com is an online research portal which facilitates the research process.

MyNetResearch helps researchers to manage their individual or collaborative research projects. Its search engine enables members to easily identify possible project collaborators with specific research interests. Researchers also have a central repository for storing documents and data that can be accessed from any location with an Internet connection. Researchers are also able to acquire knowledge from forums, blogs, short articles, and RSS feeds. MyNetResearch provide members with research tools such as Literature Search and Citation Analyzer, Journal/Conference/Grants/ Selection Guide, Research Methods Adviser, Online Survey Manager and a Bibliography creator.
